title: United Kingdom Imports of Man-made Filaments
description: Imports of Man-made Filaments in the United Kingdom increased to 51.49 GBP Million in September from 45.67 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Man-made Filaments in the United Kingdom averaged 49.72 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 83.11 GBP Million in March of 2000 and a record low of 19.67 GBP Million in May of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Man-made Filaments.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
